        <p>
         <font size="4">
          Target Participants:
         </font>
         <br />
         Line managers and supervisors who manage down-line employees, Department heads, Executives and fresh graduates who aspire to build a career in HRM, HR practitioners
         <br />
         <br />
         <font size="4">
          Methodology:
         </font>
         <br />
         mini lectures, group discussions and syndicate work
         <br />
         <br />
         <font size="4">
          Administrative details:
         </font>
         <br />
         •    Duration    : 2 days
         <br />
         •    Time        : 9.00am – 5.00pm
